snippet.title: Cities: VR | Alpha Gameplay (Meta Quest 2 / Captured on PC)
snippet.description:
Creative Director Erik Odeldahl show some Alpha footage and explain why you should be excited to play Cities: VR on the Meta Quest 2 this coming Spring!
